high_descs: Turn  left and walk up to the left sink
Open the left cabinet below the left sink and remove the dirty rag
Walk slightly right then turn back left to face the left sink
Wash the rag in the sink and remove it
Turn left and walk over to the toilet left of the counter
Put the rag on top of the back of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Put the washed rag on the toilet

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the tub, then turn left and walk up to the counter.
Open the leftmost cabinet door below the counter and take out the dirty rag, then close the cabinet door.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the dirty rag in the left side of the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean rag.
Walk over to the toilet that is to the left of the counter.
Put the clean rag on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean rag on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Take a rag out of the cabinet under the sink.
Turn and go to the sink.
Wash the rag in the sink.
Turn and go to the toilet
Put the rag on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move a washed rag to the toilet.
